OL,10,CG1978FThe RTE One and RTE 2 Cairn Hill
OL,11,F625-line UHF transmitters are brought
OL,12,Finto service. This was the first UHF
OL,13,Ftransmitter to be opened in the
OL,14,FRepublic of Ireland. At its launch, it
OL,15,Fwas the most powerful transmitter in
OL,16,Fthe country - at 800KW.
